The langtools/make/build.xml script has been adjusted to the modularized layout as part of:
http://hg.openjdk.java.net/jdk9/jdk9/langtools/rev/10fc81ac75b4

But the current script requires ant 1.9.4 to run, and generally could be improved to better fit into the modularized world, while removing obsolete/unneeded features from the script.